   -99.0  0.0045  0.0050  Optimum Seed Conc  (emergence, 1st flower, full seed) OPTSDP-EM,OPTSDP-FF,OPTSDP-FS

   -99.0   -99.0   -99.0  Minimum Shoot Conc (emergence, 1st flower, full seed) MINSHTP-EM,MINSHTP-FF,MINSHTP-FS
